---
const items = [
  '13 built-in themes, fully re-themeable',
  'Pinned slash commands in the composer',
  'Native <code>/review</code>, <code>/plan</code>, <code>/compact</code>, <code>/usage</code>',
  'Stable + nightly update channels',
  'Drag-and-drop file attachments',
  'SCM status persistence + PR integration',
  'Typewriter-style streaming reveal',
  'MCP server supervision + connectors',
  'Conversation forking + rollback per turn',
  'Cmd/Ctrl+F search across the chat session',
  'Localized UI for non-English users',
];
---

<section class="andmore">
  <div class="andmore-inner">
    <div>
      <h2>And more, quietly.</h2>
      <p class="lede">A lot of small things that add up over a long week of use.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="andmore-list">
      {items.map((item) => (
        <li>
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span set:html={item} />
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
